== Getting Ready ==
Before you begin this procedure, be sure to complete the following prerequisites: 
* Install [https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi Maven].
* Install a GitHub client. 
* Create an account at [https://github.com GitHub].
* Create an account at [https://bitbucket.org Bitbucket].

